height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"bb7112cf-7853-df49-9aee-10fbfd718319","name":"Note: Segment Audience"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Wait Before Step 2 · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,280],"id":"3d0d0700-9226-4a03-60c2-41203dff1707","name":"Note: Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag for Slow Nurture\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,880],"id":"4d98e84b-3694-7adf-adf2-802d8a4ed188","name":"Note: Tag for Slow Nurture"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Wait Before Step 2\n\nPauses 2 days — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Converted Already?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"cdcd89e8-9819-a400-b22b-a21dc8ebb697","name":"Note: Wait Before Step 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Converted Already?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.status }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail) · ②→ Mark Converted — Stop Drip","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"8a0ac693-de7b-41c2-07df-00b42ec03d25","name":"Note: Converted Already?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Update Drip Status · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"0baab92c-e940-cfd5-0086-68685ef9de0f","name":"Note: Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Converted — Stop Drip\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"c9275ae1-25e4-9a78-5cbb-f6b7e239a285","name":"Note: Mark Converted — Stop Drip"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Drip Status\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"fc17ca13-e732-9883-dfda-81fb75b1089b","name":"Note: Update Drip Status"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"737d89f0-55c1-6a2a-785c-7e813202fba6","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"bc2a4f7a-2129-52fe-544b-cf467929f640","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"c3a1b15a-6fdf-2b94-d0f7-140f1f29c02b","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"61dba3e7-4d04-f3ba-4c88-b5faaf955391","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"015bfc93-1f00-de52-cb8c-9e51732c652f","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"e3f78de7-1880-be7a-459e-ae32795e23d7","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"bd3dce94-ceed-15f8-02a4-5231b5c8a93d","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,1540],"id":"06496827-3fcd-0213-25d2-97dafa61dffd","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"72b86393-c2ed-d61c-084a-bc942794f0ef","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,1540],"id":"4ee84cb5-88b0-4bfb-38ae-a4469e554454","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Onboard new hires with Asana and Gmail\n\n**Pattern:** Onboarding Sequence · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nOnboard new hires with Asana and Gmail. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual standups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Keep Valid Tasks → Segment Audience → Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail) → Wait Before Step 2 → Converted Already? → Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to onboarding sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating standups in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"b7237c1c-7a19-89cc-f0f4-412e34ba5062","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"859304b5-661e-7064-96c7-f8124516ebba","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"41116ef5-6362-c61b-4dc7-b201b511fc26","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"7e8f4a4f-b5df-3f2d-4832-112a9b1d92e7","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your standups process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"9ebd6b9e-baf7-721d-e3f0-ba6228107bfe","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Tasks","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Tasks":{"main":[[{"node":"Segment Audience","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Segment Audience":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Tag for Slow Nurture","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)":{"main":[[{"node":"Wait Before Step 2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Wait Before Step 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Converted Already?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Converted Already?":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Mark Converted — Stop Drip","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Drip Status","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Drip Status":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag for Slow Nurture":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark Converted — Stop Drip":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"2ae52200-1f17-42c4-8ca1-00f28414b106","id":"FDX08661"}